CAUTION - EXTERNAL: 
Chambers, 
The Government has been alerted that the filing at Dkt. No. 453 contains a redaction error in which the name of a witness 
whose identity has been redacted appears. (See Dkt. No. 453 at 11). If the Court would direct the Clerks Office to remove 
the filing from ECF for the moment, the Government can submit a corrected version today. 
Thank you, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
1 Saint Andrews Plaza 
New York, New York 10007 
CAUTION - EXTERNAL EMAIL: This email originated outside the Judiciary. Exercise caution when opening 
attachments or clicking on links. 
EFTA00010103
